| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6928 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 24116ea5-e4ba-54bf-9f0e-84bd1e10f783"
